---
import Legal from '../layouts/Legal.astro';
import { social } from '../data/site';
const email = social.email || 'hello@jaindisha.in';
---

<Legal
  title="Refund & Cancellation Policy"
  updated="10 June 2026"
  description="Rescheduling, cancellation and refund terms for sessions booked with Disha Jain."
>
  <p>
    I want booking to feel fair and low-pressure. Here is how rescheduling, cancellations and
    refunds work for sessions booked through <strong>jaindisha.in</strong>.
  </p>

  <h2>Rescheduling</h2>
  <p>
    Life happens. You can reschedule a session <strong>once</strong>, up to <strong>24 hours</strong>
    before its start time, at no charge and subject to availability.
  </p>

  <h2>Cancellations and refunds</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>More than 24 hours before</strong> your session: full refund, or reschedule, whichever you prefer.</li>
    <li><strong>Within 24 hours, or a no-show</strong>: 50% of the booking amount is refunded; the remaining 50% is retained, as the slot was held for you.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Multi-session packages</h2>
  <p>
    Multi-session packages (for example the 3-session series) follow the same policy. Unused sessions
    are refunded on a pro-rata basis, less any sessions already completed, and the 24-hour or no-show
    rule above applies to the next scheduled session.
  </p>

  <h2>If I need to cancel</h2>
  <p>
    If I ever have to cancel or move a session, you will always be offered a reschedule or a full
    refund, your choice.
  </p>

  <h2>How refunds are processed</h2>
  <p>
    Approved refunds are returned to your original payment method through Razorpay, and usually
    reach you within <strong>5 to 7 business days</strong>.
  </p>

  <h2>How to request</h2>
  <p>
    Email me at <a href={`mailto:${email}`}>{email}</a> with your booking details and I will sort
    it out.
  </p>
</Legal>
